fn_tests.input_infer:
test input ranges: 
1. src as array of u8 with length 0 to 256 (inclusive) for panic scenarios
2. src as owned String with length 0 to 256 (inclusive) for valid HeaderNames
3. src as &str with non-empty values containing valid ASCII characters for non-panicking return values
4. src as &'static str with length 0 to 256 (inclusive) where all strings are valid static HeaderNames.
